ell Jr.|Carroll Campbell]]\n|[[South Carolina]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1994\u20131995\n|[[Howard Dean]]\n|[[Vermont]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1995\u20131996\n|[[Tommy Thompson]]\n|[[Wisconsin]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1996\u20131997\n|[[Bob Miller (Nevada governor)|Bob Miller]]\n|[[Nevada]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1997\u20131998\n|[[George Voinovich]]\n|[[Ohio]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|1998\u20131999\n|[[Tom Carper]]\n|[[Delaware]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|1999\u20132000\n|[[Mike Leavitt]]\n|[[Utah]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2000\u20132001\n|[[Parris Glendening]]\n|[[Maryland]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2001\u20132002\n|[[John Engler]]\n|[[Michigan]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2002\u20132003\n|[[Paul E. Patton|Paul Patton]]\n|[[Kentucky]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2003\u20132004\n|[[Dirk Kempthorne]]\n|[[Idaho]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2004\u20132005\n|[[Mark Warner]]\n|[[Virginia]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2005\u20132006\n|[[Mike Huckabee]]\n|[[Arkansas]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2006\u20132007\n|[[Janet Napolitano]]\n|[[Arizona]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2007\u20132008\n|[[Tim Pawlenty]]\n|[[Minnesota]]\n|[[Republican Party (United States)|Republican]]\n|- bgcolor=#DDEEFF\n|2008\u20132009\n|[[Ed Rendell]]\n|[[Pennsylvania]]\n|[[Democratic Party (United States)|Democratic]]\n|- bgcolor=#FFE8E8\n|2009\u20132010\n|[[Ji